                        <h2>Master your servers</h2>
                        <p>
                            ContainEye is an all-in-one tool for developers and sysadmins who need to manage their infrastructure from anywhere. Built with a focus on speed, security, and a touch of whimsy.
                        </p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Native SSH terminal with custom command suggestions.</li>
                            <li>Real-time Docker container management (Start, Stop, Restart, Logs).</li>
                            <li>Automated health checks and server monitoring.</li>
                            <li>iCloud sync and secure credential storage.</li>
                            <li>Deep Apple Shortcuts integration for advanced workflows.</li>
                        </ul>
